Q4KZNxV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ4KZNxV.png&h=d6462b55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEKZNxV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEKZNxV.png&h=7f3f6020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pQFx1Gf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpQFx1Gf.png&h=a6a96e25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前「連燈力」大將 呂布剩餘<span class=\"red\">775.34</span>HP (預計) 累計虧損<span class=\"red\">-22.47</span>%<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」基金 第二十四波操作意見收集<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」呂布軍成立只為了股東日日有燒賣食，穩健投資，為燒賣舖進發。<br />\n<br />\n一軍為短期戰線Daytrade陷陣營，二軍為呂布親領赤兔部隊。<br />\n請諸將及軍師團註明兩軍進軍方向提議<br />\n<br />\n1. 本次軍議操作為ALL IN制， 收集此帖巴打軍師將領意見<br />\n2. 收集軍師兵士們之股票後奉先設下<span class=\"red\">點將台</span>再聽天由命買入。<br />\n3. 一軍買入時間預計為<span class=\"red\">盤前16:00</span>。<br />\n4. 二軍赤兔隊無限期反省中，不定期再次進軍<br />\n5. 一軍陷陣營賣出時機分為&darr;<br />\na. 到達預計賣出時間為盤前21:00、盤後07:45或開市緊急調動<br />\nb. 增幅到達7%將立即設下5%止蝕位保存勝仗<br />\nc. 10%止賺及止蝕位，若為QQQ 上下限改為3%。<br />\n6. 若陷陣營該次結算資金增長5% 隨機選中買入股票巴打派發Payme燒賣一串<br />\n7. 呂布將保留最終決定權<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4UR2XWx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UR2XWx.jpg&h=9062ad7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次股東大會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2430824/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2430824/page/1</a><br />\n第二十二次股東大會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2460685/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2460685/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"green\"><span class=\"xx-large\">呂布曰：膠龍游淺水，我屌你老母</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S5vmUU9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS5vmUU9.png&h=c452f2f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呂布誤中奸計，武力100 智力70操盤，請絕對相信本將軍判斷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4vyLH8F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4vyLH8F.jpg&h=6f120297&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:11:55.000Z","msg":"智力冇可能長期高過70，<br />\n50才合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b221fad89a08ad16395a3d2dab5e36da8d2cc1","tid":2462322,"uid":189269,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"36801e10853def271630468e0aaa1a4dc509e502","tid":2462322,"uid":149018,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:09:47.000Z","msg":"點將台<br />\nNike GME<br />\n(奉先想撐Nike)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:17:08.000Z","msg":"臣以為共匪欺人太甚，剿匪乃順天之道，故入Nike冇得輸矣"},{"pid":"2a0458a30030907ef8d1d365d1b6c23c11103674","tid":2462322,"uid":226296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f91cb48e5ea31ded2c6a5c2cd27cabc8b837c2cf","tid":2462322,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9158f7e4dda1ecec67f0d07dee053788c91d7c6d","tid":2462322,"uid":90791,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:38:36.000Z","msg":"Gme 將軍 你次次都唔聽忠言<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:49:03.000Z","msg":"琴日好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:18:05.000Z","msg":"唔聽陳宮話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb50e99c297b1384c9d159495ea7b2a86ae0cbb6","tid":2462322,"uid":18085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36801e10853def271630468e0aaa1a4dc509e502","tid":2462322,"uid":149018,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:09:47.000Z","msg":"點將台<br />\nNike GME<br />\n(奉先想撐Nike)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:19:51.000Z","msg":"將軍 出兵gme百戰百勝 為何捨易取難<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e6db9e429730980d01ebd78ca60681d31dad8b","tid":2462322,"uid":346724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9158f7e4dda1ecec67f0d07dee053788c91d7c6d","tid":2462322,"uid":90791,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"c